<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/405200-do-i-have-to-read-the-series-from-the">do I have to read the series from the beginning to understand this novel ?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_405200'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F93947.Simple_Genius">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/405200-do-i-have-to-read-the-series-from-the">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/405200-do-i-have-to-read-the-series-from-the">Add your answer</a>
</li>
