</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/3786225-robin-j"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1371516844i/3786225._UY100_CR25,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/3786225-robin-j">Robin J</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
Baldacci has several series. In this one, I think you will certainly understand it better if you start at the beginning. 
</span>
</div>
