<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/372209-it-s-been-a-while-since-i-read-hour-game">It&#39;s been a while since I read Hour Game. I&#39;m trying to read Simple Genius. Without going back and rereading Hour Game, I can&#39;t recall anything in there that would cause Michelle Maxwell to lose her nut in this book. She was in love with a serial killer. Wow. Did I totally miss that?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_372209'><a id="like_count_community_question_372209" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/372209?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F93947.Simple_Genius">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/372209-it-s-been-a-while-since-i-read-hour-game">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/372209-it-s-been-a-while-since-i-read-hour-game">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

