        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1987976303" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8226873922633618991">This book had a very interesting twist in it compared to Baldacci&apos;s usual! The book was still intriguing and interesting, and different concepts needed to take place. Never mind that the author totally missed described and misrepresented NP complete (I have a Masters degree in theoretical computer science), but it was totally inconsequential to the story itself. This is the second book I&apos;ve read lately that had encryption as a main plot point :-). Overall, the interaction of the characters and t</span>
  <span id="freeText8226873922633618991" style="display:none">This book had a very interesting twist in it compared to Baldacci's usual! The book was still intriguing and interesting, and different concepts needed to take place. Never mind that the author totally missed described and misrepresented NP complete (I have a Masters degree in theoretical computer science), but it was totally inconsequential to the story itself. This is the second book I've read lately that had encryption as a main plot point :-). Overall, the interaction of the characters and the plot were wonderful! Another success by David Baldacci!</span>
  <a data-text-id="8226873922633618991" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


